Dextromethorphan is better known as cough syrup, but it blocks NMDA (like #ketamine) and is aiming for FDA approval in depression. In this RCT, it successfully augmented bupropion in major #depression (compared to bupropion+placebo). It's available OTC. 
https://t.co/TwOgAwfpXt https://t.co/LDDXbApUbF

The Black Dog

Comes creeping around
Head held low
Hoping to steal
The last morsels

Giving me no rest
Curse this Black Dog
Loosed from Hell
To harry the living
